data.description: This spacious home in the Bay Pointe neighborhood of Plantation Bay offers over 3200 square feet of living area, providing  ample room for entertaining guests or accommodating a large family. The main floor features a sunken living room with high ceilings, providing a grand and airy atmosphere. From here, you can enjoy views of the lanai, pool area, and golf course. Additionally, there is a formal dining room for special occasions and an eat-in kitchen with a large island that opens to the family room. The family room is equipped with a wet bar, adding convenience for hosting gatherings. Florida living is enhanced by the large screened-in lanai and private pool. The master suite is located on the first floor, and 2 additional en suites on the second level as well as an extra loft area.
